    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Patris et Filii et Spiritus Sancti. Anno Deo propicio pontificatus
                        vero dominus Victor summo pontifice et huniversalis pape in apostolica
                        sacratissima beati Petri apostoli Domini sede anno tercio, imperatore nondum
                        abemus, die primo mensis ienuarius, indictione decima, in <placeName
                            ref="#places/4179">Ponposia</placeName>. Petimus ad vobis dominus
                            <persName key="#Priests #Abbots #Monks" ref="#people/1597"
                            >Albizo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> atque <rs key="#Monks">monachus</rs> atque
                            <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> regule <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Production #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Hay/fodder #Linen #Rent_in_money #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie quod vocatur in
                            Ponpose</orgName>, una per consensum et auctoritatem deserviencium
                        eiusdem monesterium, uti nobis in Dei nomine <persName><name ref="Petrus"
                                >Petrus</name></persName> qui vocatur de … et <persName><name
                                ref="Albegunda">Albegunda</name></persName> iugale nostrisque filiis
                        et heredibus, idest medietatem de uno <rs key="#Casalia">casale</rs> cum <rs
                            key="#Houses">casa</rs> super se abente, in latitudine sua <rs
                            key="#Size">pedes cinquanta et quinque</rs>: uno latere <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Priests"><name ref="Adam de Dominico">Adammo de
                                Dominucus</name></persName> presbiter, secundo latere <persName
                            key="#Confinia"><name ref="Iohannes/Bullifaba">Iohannes qui vocatur
                                Bullifaba</name></persName>, da uno caput <placeName
                            key="#Confinia #Rivers" ref="#places/3563">Gauro</placeName> et da alio
                        caput percorrente in <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">valle</rs>; et
                        medietatem de una <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">masaricia</rs> que
                        fuit de <persName key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"><name ref="Albertinus"
                                >Albertino</name></persName> in integrum, de omnes res, sortes et
                        portiones quanta abuit et detinuit in <placeName ref="#places/4685"
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Production #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Hay/fodder #Linen #Rent_in_money #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >Medio Gauro</placeName> ad iure monasterio vestro infra totum <rs
                            key="#Fundi">fundum</rs> qui vocatur <geogName ref="#estates/3926"
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Production #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Hay/fodder #Linen #Rent_in_money #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/3596"
                                key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Houses #Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fundi #Casalia #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Penalty #Production #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Legumes #Wine #Hay/fodder #Linen #Rent_in_money #Levies #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                                >Gauro</placeName></geogName> cultare laborare potueritis de ipsa
                        res que ad rem medietatem parteque pertinentibus vel subiacentibus,
                        interrafines eius latere secundum alio libello de Medio Gauro. Que omnia cum
                            <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> et <rs key="#Cereals"
                            >campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pradis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder"
                            >pascuis</rs>, <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>, <rs>salectis</rs>,
                            <rs>sacionalibus</rs>, <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                            >padulibus</rs>, <rs key="#Fisheries">piscacionibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">venacionibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">aucupacionibus</rs> suis
                        cum ingressis et egresso suo et cum omnibus que ad supradictas res
                        pertinentibus vel subiacentibus sicut supra legitur, hec omnia concedo nobis
                        abendum, tenendum, possidendum, laborandum, supersedendum, defensandum et in
                        omnibus meliorandum in annis advenientibus viinti et nove ad renovandum <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">libellum</rs> renovemus. Ita sane
                        ut inferatis domnice rationibus vos ad vestrisque subcessoribus rendere
                        debeamus singulis quibusque annis de <rs key="#Production">terra
                            laboratoria</rs>, hoc est <rs key="#Levies">terratico</rs> de <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Maiores">grano</rs> et de <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores"
                            >sicale</rs> et <rs key="#Legumes">faba</rs> in campo capa secunda,
                        secundum alio libellum … modio septimo, <rs key="#Linen">lino</rs> manna
                        octava; et si <rs key="#Wine">vineam</rs> pastenaveritis [extra] casale
                        fruere debeatis … annis quinque et postea redere debeatis secundum altero
                        libello; et si rongaverimus de valle, fruere debeatis annis … et postea
                        redere debeamus sicut de cetera terra; pensionem … <rs key="#Rent_in_money"
                            >Veneticorum sex</rs> omnique anno tritulatum adque pervectum in … per
                        nos petitoris usque ad supradicto monasterio vestro, quando <rs
                            key="#Cereals">blavas</rs> venerit ad tollendum cum onore et obediencia.
                        Et non abeamus licentiam de supradictas res ad nullo placito publicum neque
                        districta andare nisi ad vos vel ad tuis subcessores. Si quis vero pras
                        vestra contra os peticione ire tentaverimus et omnia que supra legitur non
                        observaverimus vel adimpleverimus, de pras parti fidem servanti ante omnis
                        litis inicium vel interpellatione, pene nomine, <rs key="#Penalty">auri
                            optimi uncie due</rs> et post pena soluta manente hoc peticionis sicut
                        supra legitur in suo robore et firmitate. Quam vero peticionis pari tenore
                        conscripto <persName key="#Tabellio"><name ref="Urbanus"
                            >Urbanus</name></persName> in Dei nomine <rs key="#Tabellio"
                            >tabellius</rs> scribendum rogavimus et huius alterius nobis pariter
                        contradimus quod consecuti estis Deum agamus et nobis massima gracias, sub
                        die et mense et indictione supradicta decima, in Ponpose. Signum manus
                        supradicto Petrus et Albigunda iugale petitoris ad omnia supradicta cui
                        relectum est.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
